57 insurance policies but obtainable through the purchase of
58 wind, wind and hail, storm or windstorm coverage, or all."
59 Section 2. This act applies to tax years beginning on
60 or after January 1, 2027.
61 Section 3. This act shall become effective on October
62 1, 2026.
